&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize &amp;amp; Consolidate Tooling:&lt;/strong&gt; Run a structured system intake model with clear SLAs, and strategically consolidate redundant software to build a leaner tech stack.&lt;/li&gt;
